      <title>法国总理称增税将影响约 300 家公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/france-s-tax-increases-to-hit-some-300-companies-premier-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 表示，为控制法国预算赤字而计划实施的增税措施将影响法国约 300 家最大的企业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/france-s-tax-increases-to-hit-some-300-companies-premier-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 19:45:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>七国集团声明草案警告中东局势“难以控制”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/draft-g-7-statement-warns-of-uncontrollable-mideast-escalation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻看到的一份声明草案显示，七国集团将警告称，危险的袭击循环“有可能加剧中东地区无法控制的升级”，并将谴责伊朗最近对以色列发动的导弹袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/draft-g-7-statement-warns-of-uncontrollable-mideast-escalation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 18:44:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙拯救欧洲的孤独使命</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/podcast-macron-s-lonely-mission-to-save-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在本期《选民经济学》中，我们讨论了法国总统对欧洲大陆竞争力丧失的警告，以及它可能很快付出的代价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/podcast-macron-s-lonely-mission-to-save-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 18:21:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德克萨斯州监管机构希望数据中心建造发电厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/texas-regulator-wants-data-centers-to-build-power-plants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州最高电力监管机构向大型科技公司传达了一个信息：如果你想在发电厂旁边建造人工智能数据中心，那么你可能也必须建造发电厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/texas-regulator-wants-data-centers-to-build-power-plants</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 18:17:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摇摆州选举官员准备迎接最后一刻的法庭诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/swing-state-election-officers-brace-for-last-minute-court-action</link>
      <description><![CDATA[9 月，北卡罗来纳州最高法院裁定，小罗伯特·F·肯尼迪 (Robert F. Kennedy Jr.) 因放弃竞选美国总统而不得出现在该州的选票上，德里克·鲍恩斯 (Derek Bowens) 不得不仓促应对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/swing-state-election-officers-brace-for-last-minute-court-action</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 18:08:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚提出新的税收优惠政策吸引天然气投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/nigeria-proposes-new-tax-incentives-to-attract-gas-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位政府官员表示，尼日利亚希望通过新的深水天然气勘探政策框架中提出的税收减免和其他措施，吸引高达 100 亿美元的新投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/nigeria-proposes-new-tax-incentives-to-attract-gas-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 16:57:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥 Sheinbaum 计划未来几年将最低工资提高 12%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/mexico-s-sheinbaum-plans-12-minimum-wage-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·希因鲍姆表示，她计划在 2025 年及随后几年将最低工资提高约 12%，这一增幅将远高于拉丁美洲第二大经济体的通货膨胀率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/mexico-s-sheinbaum-plans-12-minimum-wage-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 16:34:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列袭击贝鲁特真主党，七国集团呼吁克制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/israel-strikes-hezbollah-as-biden-comments-send-oil-surging</link>
      <description><![CDATA[七国集团警告称，中东局势不要陷入不受控制的升级循环。以色列称，周四轰炸了贝鲁特十多个真主党目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/israel-strikes-hezbollah-as-biden-comments-send-oil-surging</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 16:30:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗实力减弱引发担忧 或将推动核武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/weakened-iran-raises-fears-it-may-make-push-for-nuclear-weapons</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数周以来，以色列不断袭击，伊朗的代理人真主党和哈马斯势力被削弱，伊朗很少像现在这样处于被动地位。而德黑兰周二向以色列发射了约 200 枚导弹，美国认为这些导弹“无效”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/weakened-iran-raises-fears-it-may-make-push-for-nuclear-weapons</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 14:59:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩尔多瓦称俄罗斯投入巨资阻挠其加入欧盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/moldova-says-russia-channeling-millions-to-thwart-its-eu-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩尔多瓦当局称，他们发现了一项由俄罗斯支持的行动，涉及 13 万名摩尔多瓦公民，旨在影响本月对总统玛雅·桑杜的欧洲愿望至关重要的投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/moldova-says-russia-channeling-millions-to-thwart-its-eu-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 12:49:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
